1. Data mgt as core infra
  Treat data with same relevance and priority as you would cloud infra or security.
  Central data governance
  implement access control and ensuring data flows are traceble and auditable.
  
2. Active data quality mechanisms
  pipeline 
  anomaly detection (automated)
  labeling standards
  monitor for drift
  
3. Synthetic data to fill gaps
  and preserve privacy
  
4. Defensive design against
  data poisoning
  source verification
  versioning
  realtime validation
  of external as well as internal data feeds
  
5. Data feedback loops
  data should not be seen as immutable in your AI systems
  It should be able to evolve and adapt over time.
  
